public abstract static class ConditionalHandler.Abstract extends ConditionalHandler
An Abstract ConditionalHandler. Implementations must provide both ConditionalHandler.onConditionsMet(Request, Response, Callback) and ConditionalHandler.onConditionsNotMet(Request, Response, Callback) implementations.
